   SimpleRequesters@{tab}Procedures to invoke various requesters with a call@{line}
   CustomGlyphs@{tab}Provides a number of Boopsi drawlist figures@{line}
   SimpleImageHandler@{tab}Provides standard and custom Boopsi image and glyph objects@{line}
   SimpleScreens@{tab}For using public screens with your app.@{line}

