  @{" SimpleGraphics " LINK "SimpleGraphics"}   @{line}

@{B}@{u}Directory Processing@{uu}@{UB}

  DirUtilsDyn@{tab}As DirUtils, but using unlimited length strings for file specifications.@{line}

