TstAutoRequest@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Calls AutoRequest and EasyRequest.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
@{_LMARG_}

@{_HEADING_ "Reaction"}
CheckBoxExample@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Reaction example translated from the SDK.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
DateBrowserExample@{tab}@{lindent 43}- <ditto>@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
FuelGaugeExample@{tab}@{lindent 43}- <ditto>@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
GetColorExample@{tab}@{lindent 43}- <ditto>@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
GlyphExample@{tab}@{lindent 43}- <ditto>@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
@{_LMARG_}

@{_HEADING_ "Compiler"}
TstZeroDivide@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Shows exception handling of a divide by zero exception.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
TstRandomNumbers@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Generates one set of ten random numbers from 0 to 99, and another from 0 to 9999.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
@{_LMARG_}

