TstArgsSupport@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Parses its argument. Template is "-file/A"@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
TstDirUtil2@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Tests GetFileSize() function from module DirUtil2.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
TstDirUtil3@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Tests AbsoluteFileSpec() function from module DirUtil3.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
TstRandInts@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Tests RandInts module distribution of x objects into y cells.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
@{_LMARG_}

@{_HEADING_ "Aglet Experimental"}
TstSimpleGUI@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Demo of some gadget windows created with module SimpleGUI.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
TstRandomBoxes@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Generates a display of a window with x boxes randomly placed and colored within it.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
TstGetFile@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Shows module SimpleRequesters access to the GetFile gadget.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
TstSimpleGraphics@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Demo of 2D drawing package layered on Amiga GraphicsLib drawing routines.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
TstSimpleImageHandler@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Shows images and glyphs supported currently in this module.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
TstSimpleMenus@{tab}@{lindent 43}-Puts up a window with NewMenus menus created by this module.@{_SMLDENT_}@{line}
